{
  "stem": "23096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And it would have killed them right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They, they couldn't have handled it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "All, all they could handle was maybe some hot water with a chicken fanned over the top of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "That's about as strong as they could as-- they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And Ohrdruf, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] even though it was a small camp, they don't know too much about it because when the Germans left, they took all their records.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And we never did find them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They think there's probably-- maybe 7,000 in the camp at one time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And out of anybody was left, there was less than 75 that we found alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I doubt if 25 survived out of the 75 because they were too far gone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I mean, you can go to a certain point.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And it's just more or less a, a point of no return on, on that type of starvation, I think.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "So many of them died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And we-- our-- I know our medics, when they came in, had no experience on stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And I, I, I can just imagine them trying to give them something to eat, which was the worst thing they could have done.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "So I-- that's one thing I always hope that at least some of them, you know, survived because [LAUGHS] we were dumb about such things like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "This is the first camp [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we came into.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, I really-- at the time, I don't-- I don't think we fully appreciate-- I hate to say appreciate-- or fully realized what we were walking into, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
